  "title": "Preschool Cook  幼儿园厨师",
  "description": "<h3><strong>About the Role</strong></h3><p><strong>关于这份工作</strong></p><p>Pebble Place is a warm and caring preschool.<br />Pebble Place 是一所温暖、有爱心的幼儿园。</p><p>We believe good food helps children grow well and feel safe.<br />我们相信，好的食物能帮助孩子健康成长，也让孩子感到安心。</p><p>We are looking for a Preschool Cook to prepare simple, healthy meals for about 50 children, keep the kitchen clean and safe, and work well with our teachers.<br />我们正在寻找一位幼儿园厨师，为大约 50 位孩子准备简单又健康的餐点，保持厨房清洁与安全，并与老师们良好配合。<br /><strong></strong></p><p><strong>What You’ll Do | 工作内容</strong></p><p>Cook balanced, child-friendly meals (breakfast, lunch, tea), with simple dietary adjustments.<br />准备营养均衡、适合孩子的餐点（早餐、午餐、下午茶），并处理简单的饮食需求。</p><p>Manage ingredients well to reduce waste, adjust to availability, and purchase stock.<br />妥善管理食材，减少浪费，根据供应情况调整，并负责采购。</p><p>Maintain food hygiene and safety (WSQ certificate required), and keep the kitchen clean.<br />遵守食品卫生与安全规定（需持有 WSQ 证书），并保持厨房清洁。</p><p>Work with educators to ensure smooth, calm, and happy mealtimes for children.<br />与老师合作，确保孩子用餐过程顺利、安静又愉快。<br /><br /><br /><strong>Who You Are | 我们希望您是</strong></p><p>Experienced in cooking for groups (preschool or childcare experience is a plus).<br />有为多人煮食的经验（有幼儿园或托育经验更佳）。</p><p>Understands basic child nutrition and holds a food hygiene certificate.<br />了解儿童基本营养，并持有食品卫生证书。</p><p>Organised, works well with others, and values kindness and growth.<br />做事有条理，能与他人合作，并重视关怀与成长。<br /></p><p><strong>Why Pebble Place? | 为什么加入 Pebble Place？</strong></p><p>Values-driven workplace with openness, growth, and respect.<br />重视价值观的工作环境，强调开放、成长与尊重。</p><p>Medical benefits and daily meals provided.<br />提供医疗福利及每日员工餐。</p><p>Full-time or part-time options available.<br />提供全职或兼职的灵活选择。</p>",
